{"Title": "PELOSI FLIES COMMERCIAL! Speaker Pelosi Spotted at Reagan Airport \u2013 Flees DC as Trump Stays at White House", "Locale": "en_US", "Desc": "Speaker of the House Nancy Pelosi (D-CA) was spotted walking through Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport late Friday afternoon with a carry-on bag on wheels....", "Textdata": ["\r\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\r\n", "Speaker of the House Nancy Pelosi (D-CA) was spotted walking through Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport late Friday afternoon with a carry-on bag on wheels. Pelosi was accompanied by at least one aide and a security detail. Meanwhile, President Donald Trump remained at the White House prepared to negotiate with Democrats on funding border wall security to reopen the partial shutdown federal government.", "Pelosi was photographed by MSNBC reporter Garrett Haake who posted a photo to Twitter with this caption, \u201cLooks like ", "@", "SpeakerPelosi", " won\u2019t be staying in DC for the weekend. She and her detail just passed me at Reagan National Airport.\u201d", "\r\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\r\n", "\n", "Looks like ", "@SpeakerPelosi", " won\u2019t be staying in DC for the weekend. She and her detail just passed me at Reagan National Airport. ", "pic.twitter.com/g2UV8hwYql", "\n", "\u2014 Garrett Haake (@GarrettHaake) ", "January 18, 2019", "\n", "Apparently, Haake did not ask Pelosi any questions, such as, \u201cwhere are you headed, Madam Speaker?\u201d, even though Pelosi left D.C. while the government is still shutdown and her departure comes a day after Trump canceled her overseas CODEL trip on a government jet.\u00a0 Haake is a Capitol Hill reporter who just spoke to Pelosi earlier Friday at a Hill presser so he is no stranger to Pelosi or her Capitol Police security detail.", "\n", ".", "@GarrettHaake", ": Do you view this as retaliation for your letter about the State of the Union?", "\n", "Speaker Pelosi: \u201cI would hope not. I don\u2019t think the president would be that petty, do you?\u201d", "\n", "Watch more: ", "https://t.co/fqZAiy4LBZ", " ", "pic.twitter.com/Z0O7aR5R3N", "\n", "\u2014 MSNBC (@MSNBC) ", "January 18, 2019", "\n", "\n", "On Capitol Hill, ", "@SpeakerPelosi", ", asked by ", "@GarrettHaake", " if cancelling her CODEL is retaliation for her SOTU letter:", "\n", "PELOSI: \u201cI don\u2019t think the president would be that petty, do you?\u201d ", "pic.twitter.com/BraU1NXi3J", "\n", "\u2014 Frank Thorp V (@frankthorp) ", "January 18, 2019", "\n", "A civilian posted that he too saw Pelosi at Reagan National and that he was not comfortable approaching her as she was in a hurry and had security.", "\n", "That thing when you\u2019re in DC at the airport and one of your CA representatives (Nancy Pelosi) walks right by you \ud83e\udd37\ud83c\udffb\u200d\u2642\ufe0f", "\n", "\u2014 DJ Jenkins (@DJJenkins) ", "January 18, 2019", "\n", "\r\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\r\n", "\n", "Haha, she was in a hurry and had 2 secret service next to her. Decided not to \ud83d\ude02", "\n", "\u2014 DJ Jenkins (@DJJenkins) ", "January 18, 2019", "\n", "Shortly after Pelosi was spotted at the airport, President Trump announced he would be making a major announcement Saturday afternoon.", "\n", "I will be making a major announcement concerning the Humanitarian Crisis on our Southern Border, and the Shutdown, tomorrow afternoon at 3 P.M., live from the ", "@WhiteHouse", ".", "\n", "\u2014 Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) ", "January 18, 2019", "\n", "Trump followed later with a video statement:", "\n", "pic.twitter.com/wjqVvTqeky", "\r\n", "\r\n", "\r\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\r\n", "\n", "\u2014 Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) ", "January 19, 2019", "\n", "The post ", "PELOSI FLIES COMMERCIAL! Speaker Pelosi Spotted at Reagan Airport \u2013 Flees DC as Trump Stays at White House", " appeared first on ", "The Gateway Pundit", "."]}
