{"Title": "HERE WE GO: House Dems Ignore Veto Threat, Pass Bill to End Shutdown Without Border Wall Funding", "Locale": "en_US", "Desc": "The Democrats weren\u2019t quite done showboating Thursday night and passed a bill to reopen the government. In a 241-190 vote, the House passed a combined...", "Textdata": ["\r\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\r\n", "The Democrats weren\u2019t quite done showboating Thursday night and passed a bill to reopen the government.", "In a 241-190 vote, the House passed a combined bill to re-open most shuttered parts of the government and it also excluded border wall funding.", "7 Republicans joined the Democrats and voted \u2018yea,\u2019 according to Fox News\u2019 Chad Pergram.", "Here is the", " list of Republicans who voted yes", ": Fitzpatrick-PA, Hurd-TX, Katko-NY, King-NY, Stefanik-NY, Upton-MI and Walden-OR.", "The measure puts together six of the seven unresolved appropriations bill in one package, reported Fox News Congress reporter Chad Pergram.", "\n", "Hse ok\u2019s combined bill to re-open most shuttered parts of the government. The vote was 241-190. 7 GOPers  joined Dems & voted yea. The measure puts together six of the seven unresolved appropriations bills in 1 package and runs those areas of the government through Sept 30", "\n", "\u2014 Chad Pergram (@ChadPergram) ", "January 4, 2019", "\n", "\r\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\r\n", "Of course this is a complete waste of time because Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell has repeatedly stated he will not bring a Democrat bill to the Senate floor that the President will not sign.", "President Trump is holding his ground and refuses to sign any bills from Congress that do not include border wall funding.", "It looks like the partial government shutdown won\u2019t be ending any time soon.", "The post ", "HERE WE GO: House Dems Ignore Veto Threat, Pass Bill to End Shutdown Without Border Wall Funding", " appeared first on ", "The Gateway Pundit", "."]}
